data.description: Elegant Newmark One-story with 4 bedrooms, 3 baths with walk in closets.  Beautiful Stucco/brick elevation.  Lots of space in this popular floorplan.  Open concept kitchen/breakfast/living area.  Separate dining area (or use as study, media room or play area). Large primary bedroom and breakfast area both have bay windows.  Second bedroom suite plus 2 more bedrooms with a shared bath.  Refrigerator stays with home.    Covered back patio and nice fenced yard large enough for your children, pets, or future pool.  Sienna is a wonderful neighborhood with multiple pools, gyms, play areas, tennis courts, golf course, equestrian center, plus outdoor and indoor gathering areas.
